Name
	Gsep - Graphics Separator
Syntax

	#include <notif.h>

	Gsep *mk(Gsep);

Inherits
	Widget

Border
	None

Size
	Width=6 Height=6

Color
	shadowtop and shadowbot are used to the line colors.

Description
	A graphics-separator, typically used for menus.  A single 3d-effect
line is drawn from end to end in the larger dimension, and centered within
the smaller dimension.
